				<h1 itemprop="headline" class="entry-title">Today in Small Business: Business Travel and Ebola</h1>
		<div class="story-meta-footer">
			<address class="byline author vcard" itemprop="author creator" itemtype="//schema.org/Person">
				By Gene Marks			</address>
			<!-- date published --><time class="dateline " datetime="2014-10-14T15:03:35+00:00" itemprop="datePublished">October 14, 2014 11:03 am</time>
			<!-- date updated --><span class="visually-hidden updated">October 14, 2014 11:03 am</span><button class="button comments-button  theme-kicker" data-skip-to-para-id="">
</button>
		</div>
			</header>
		<div class="entry-content"><div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/10/14/today-in-small-business-business-travel-and-ebola/" data-title="Today in Small Business: Business Travel and Ebola" data-description="How to transfer money through Twitter. How to get the most out of Yelp. Is this the hottest real estate start-up in New York City?">
				<div class="ad sharetools-inline-article-ad"></div>
				<div id="MiddleLeft" class="ad middle-left-ad nocontent robots-nocontent"></div>
				</div><div class="inlineModule"><div class="entry"><h6 class="kicker"><a href="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/category/dashboard/">Dashboard</a></h6><p class="summary">A daily roundup of small-business developments.</p></div></div>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">Whatâs affecting me, my clients and other small-business owners today.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>The Economy</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Here&#8217;s how to calculate <a href="//dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/10/13/calculating-the-grim-costs-of-ebola/">the grim costs of the Ebola</a> outbreak.</li>
<li>Is Silicon Valley <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/10/13/opinion/will-boom-lead-to-bust-in-silicon-valley.html">headed for another bust</a>?</li>
<li>Ford plans to <a href="//news.yahoo.com/ford-add-850-jobs-dearborn-factories-f-150-135750644--finance.html">add 850 jobs</a> at its Dearborn, Mich., factories to build F-150 trucks (which have been popular with small businesses).</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Business Travel</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>The <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/10/14/business/for-travelers-ebola-represents-a-small-blip-on-the-radar.html">impact of Ebola on business travel</a> has been minor so far.</li>
<li>Here&#8217;s a common-sense approach to <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/10/14/business/a-common-sense-approach-to-fighting-in-flight-germs.html">fighting in-flight germs</a>.</li>
<li>Here are the countries <a href="//www.businessinsider.com/where-ebola-will-spread-2014-10">where Ebola</a> will probably show up next.</li>
<li>A flight attendants union is <a href="//online.wsj.com/articles/flight-attendants-fight-to-reinstate-ban-on-fliers-devices-1412975553">suing to reinstate</a> the ban on electronic devices on airplanes.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Start-Up</strong></p>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>Is this the <a href="//www.alleywatch.com/2014/10/looking-for-a-new-place-this-nyc-startup-gives-you-the-prices-and-the-costs/">hottest real estate start-up</a> in New York City?</li>
</ul>
</ul>
