<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Entrepreneurship</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>A <a href="//www.inc.com/business-insider/this-20-year-old-entrepreneur-owns-a-chinese-factory.html">20-year-old entrepreneur</a> expects his consumer-products company to gross about $10 million in revenue and now owns a factory in China.</li>
<li>A <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/10/14/business/stolen-wallet-leads-to-valuable-lesson-for-entrepreneur.html?">stolen wallet</a> turns into a valuable lesson for an entrepreneur.</li>
