<li>Samsung says it <a href="//www.fastcompany.com/3037038/fast-feed/samsung-says-it-has-developed-wi-fi-tech-thats-10-times-faster?partner=rss">has developed</a> a Wi-Fi technology that&#8217;s 10 times faster.</li>
